#
#  Text 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

Brian is attempting to high jump over a crossbar set at [`[$hc]`] [`m`]. At the instant of takeoff (when he is no longer in contact with the ground) his vertical velocity is [`[$v]`] [`m/s`], and his center of gravity is [`[$cog]`] [`m`] high.

*a)* What is Brian's vertical acceleration at the instant of takeoff?

[`a_y=`] [_____]{"$ay"} [`m/s^2`]  

*b)* How much time elapses after takeoff until Brian reaches his peak height?

[`t=`] [_____]{"$t"} [`s`]  

*c)* What peak height does Brian's center of gravity achieve?

[`y_{peak}=`] [_____]{"$h"} [`m`]  

END_PGML

